<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣ - وَوَهْمُهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٤ - وَمُخَالَفَتُهُ لِلثِّقَاتِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٥ - وَسُوءُ حِفْظِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَالْوَهْمُ:</span> كَوَصْلِ مُرْسِلٍ، وَإِدْخَالِ حَدِيثٍ فيِ حَدِيثٍ؛ وَهَذَا هُوَ الْمُعَلَّلُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">والْمُخَالَفَةُ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>إِنْ كَانَتُ بِتَغَيْيِرِ سِيَاقِ الْإِسْنَادِ؛ فَهُوَ مُدْرَجُ الْإِسْنَادِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>أَوْ بِدَرْجِ مَوْقُوفٍ بِمَرْفُوعٍ؛ فَهُوَ مُدْرَجُ الْمَتْنِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>أَوْ بِتَقْدِيِمٍ وتَأْخِيرٍ فِي الْأَسْماَءِ؛ فَهُوَ الْمَقْلُوبُ، وَقَدْ يَقَعُ الْقَلْبُ فِي الْمَتْنِ أَيْضًا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَوْ بِزِيَادَةِ رَاوٍ؛ فَهُوَ الْمَزِيدُ فِي مُتَّصِلِ الْأَسَانِيدِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>أَوْ بِإِبْدَالِ رَاوٍ، وَلَا مُرَجِّحَ؛ فَهُوَ المُضْطَرِبُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">أَوْ بِتَغْيِيِر بَعْضِ الْحُرُوفِ بِالْنِّسْبَةِ إِلَى النَّقْطِ:</span> هُوَ الْمُصَحَّفُ،<span class="c5"> وَبِالنِّسْبَةِ إِلَى الشَّكْلِ:</span> هُوَ المُحَرَّفُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وَالْإِسْنَادُ:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">إِنِ انْتَهَى إِلَى النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> فَالْمرْفُوعُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">أَوْ إِلَى الصَّحَابِيِّ:</span> فَالْموْقُوفُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>أَوْ إِلَى التَّابِعِيِّ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ منْ دُونَهُ:</span> فَالْمَقْطُوعُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>